/****************************************************************/
/* cuda3dfdm acronym stands for:                                */
/*                                                              */
/* CUDA - NVidia Cuda                                           */
/* 3d - mainly 3 spatial dimensionsionality is considered       */
/* fdm - Finite Differnce Method                                */
/*                                                              */
/* However it focuses on dynamical solution of Poisson equation */
/* (heat equation, diffusion equation). It works on NVidia      */
/* CUDA supported GPU devices (tested down to 1.3cc). Up to now */
/* only explicit method is developed, implicit and              */
/* Crank-Nicholson (demanding linear system solver for each     */
/* step ) are planned to be included in future.                 */
/*                                                              */
/****************************************************************/
